AI Flashcards API Documentation

http://127.0.0.1:8000


Generate Flashcards 

URL: /flashcards
Method: Post
Description: Create a group of flashcards.
Request Parameters
No parameters needed
Request Body Object Structure:
No request object needed.
Response Object Structure:

[
  {
    "text": string,
    "difficulty": string,
    "card_amount":  integer,
  {
[


Reponse Example:

[
  { 
    "id": 1,
    "question": "What is 7+3?",
    "answer": "3"
  },
  {
     "id": 2,
    "question": "What is Georgia's Capitol",
    "answer": "Atlanta"
  },
  {
     "id": 3,
    "question": "Whats the largest Ocean?",
    "answer": "Pacific Ocean"
  },
  {
     "id": 4,
    "question": "What is the shortened name for the element Iridium ",
    "answer": "IR"
  },
  {
     "id": 5,
    "question": "Who created the company Microsoft",
    "answer": "Bill Gates"
  },
]

Get Flashcards 

URL: /flashcards/{ID}
Method: Get
Description: Gets a single flashcard from list
Request Parameters
No parameters needed
Request Body Object Structure:
No request object needed.
Response Object Structure:

[
  {
    "text": string,
    "difficulty": string,
    "card_amount":  integer,
  {
[



Reponse Example:

[
  { 
    "id": 1,
    "question": "What is 7+3?",
    "answer": "3"
  },
]


